 through front street the company is engaged in the business of providing longterm reinsurance including reinsurance to the specialty insurance sector of fixed deferred and payout annuities the companys subsidiary fidelity  guaranty life fgl provides life insurance and annuity products fgl also sells single premium immediate annuities spias which provide a series of periodic payments for a fixed period of time or for the life of the policyholder the companys subsidiaries also include fs holdco ii ltd hgi asset management holdings llc hgi energy holdings llc and hgi funding llcspectrum brands manufactures markets andor distributes its products in approximately  countries in the north america na europe middle east and africa emea latin america latam and asiapacific apac regions through a range of trade channels including retailers wholesalers and distributors original equipment manufacturers oems construction companies and hearing aid professionals spectrum brands offers five product lines global batteries  appliances gba hardware  home improvement hhi global pet supplies pet home and garden hg and global auto care gacthe company competes with energizer holdings inc berkshire hathaway matsushita newell brands general electric delonghi america sharkninja nacco industries seb sa whirlpool corporation conair corporate koninklijke philips nv glen dimplex the procter  gamble company wahl clipper corporation helen of troy limited allegion the hillman group hampton hardware crown bolt kohler masco fortune brands american standard glacier bay aquasource mars corporation the hartz mountain corporation central garden  pet company the scotts miraclegro company bayer ag sc johnson  son inc henkel ag  co kgaa valvoline prestone turtle wax black magic mothers meguiars lucas sea foam athene life re ltd global atlantic financial group limited guggenheim life and annuity company reinsurance group of america incorporated legal  general reinsurance company ltd and resolution life holdin